The dataset used for the experiment is taken from " Tensorflow for poets example"(Flower dataset).

You can directly download the dataset from http://download.tensorflow.org/example_images/flower_photos.tgz

packages required:-
1) tensorflow(1.13)
2) opencv (3.4.x)
3) numpy
4) tqdm

download the dataset and provide the ath of the dataset in the path present in the colorize.py script

The waste_colorize_kl directory is the collection of output from each and every epochs. In this experiment, I have ran approx 1130 epochs. Try running more for better otcome.

Happy experimenting!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
